@TOC ARexx
@TITLE "Digits ARexx Error Codes"

@{fg background}@{bg text} ARexx Error Codes @{fg text}@{bg background}

0  = No Errors.
11 = Syntax error in command.
12 = Unknown command.
20 = Out of memory.
@ENDNODE

